Per la parte di pretrattamento useremo AmpWrap (https://github.com/LDoni/AmpWrap),

In particolare il modulo illumina 



Workflow

    Initial quality control with FastQC and QC report generation with MultiQC
    Primer removal from sequencing reads with Cutadapt. The --discard-untrimmed option is applied
    Post-cutadapt quality control with FastQC and QC report generation with MultiQC
    Determine optimal trimming parameters for DADA2 with FIGARO
    Amplicon sequence variant inference with DADA2

